{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.560", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.800", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir reden jetzt zum zweiten Mal innerhalb von 24\u00a0Stunden \u00fcber die Abschaffung des Solis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.080", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir haben gelernt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.080", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Unterschied zwischen der AfD und der FDP besteht in 365\u00a0Tagen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.800", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die FDP m\u00f6chte den Soli ein Jahr sp\u00e4ter abschaffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestern habe ich erl\u00e4utert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.360", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum die Abschaffung aus Sicht der AfD durchaus sinnvoll ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie versch\u00e4rft die soziale Schieflage und den Investitionsstau in diesem Lande. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.000", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist zwar schlecht f\u00fcr Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.920", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es ist nat\u00fcrlich Wasser auf Ihre populistischen M\u00fchlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.360", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und darauf kommt es Ihnen an."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.360", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es stellt sich aber die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum die FDP dabei mitmacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.440", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum macht sie sich jetzt selber so klein und zum Steigb\u00fcgelhalter der AfD?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.160", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe den Eindruck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.360", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen einfach nicht anders."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ich mache heute weiter."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.360", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die neue FDP ist schlichtweg die alte FDP. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.920", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So einfach ist das. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.960", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind die Partei der Klientelpolitik."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.120", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt vielleicht einen Unterschied: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.080", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die M\u00f6venpick-Steuer hat 2009 nur 1\u00a0Milliarde Euro gekostet; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.160", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit diesem Antrag aber wollen Sie\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.720", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und damit wollten Sie uns auch in den Jamaika-Verhandlungen erpressen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.880", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihrer Klientel der Reichen und Besserverdienenden ein 20-Milliarden-Euro-Steuergeschenk machen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.800", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am Dienstag beschwerte sich Herr Lindner\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.880", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich habe es geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "manche t\u00e4ten so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.880", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als wenn nur die Geissens dieser Welt gerettet werden sollten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.360", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dass nur die von der Abschaffung des Soli profitieren w\u00fcrden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.680", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stimme ja nicht.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann nehmen wir doch einmal die Geissens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.520", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie stark w\u00fcrden sie denn profitieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.480", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie ihren Wohnsitz in Deutschland h\u00e4tten?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.000", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.080", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist ganz einfach: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.920", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach Aussage des \u201eVerm\u00f6genMagazins\u201c haben die Geissens zurzeit ein normales Einkommen in H\u00f6he von 2\u00a0Millionen Euro im Jahr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.880", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei diesem Einkommen m\u00fcssten sie in der Tat 50\u00a0000\u00a0Euro weniger Steuern im Jahr zahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.920", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir Ihrem Vorschlag folgten und den Soli abschafften. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.120", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen wir einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was eine Familie ebenfalls mit zwei Kindern und einem Jahreseinkommen in H\u00f6he von 50\u00a0000\u00a0Euro von der Abschaffung des Soli h\u00e4tte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Familie profitierte null Euro von einer solchen Abschaffung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.120", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das ist das Problem."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Wahrheit ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.200", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die FDP will den 20\u00a0Prozent Deutschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.440", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die am besten verdienen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.360", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "80\u00a0Prozent der Entlastung zuschustern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.360", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie verkaufen das auch noch als Wohltat f\u00fcr das ganze Land. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.200", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6ren Sie endlich auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.880", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die deutsche Bev\u00f6lkerung f\u00fcr dumm zu verkaufen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe noch einen Tipp f\u00fcr Sie von der kleinen GroKo. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.040", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnten Ihren missgl\u00fcckten Start korrigieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.520", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.800", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "statt den Soli um 10\u00a0Milliarden Euro abzusenken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem Geld den Hartz-IV-Regelsatz nur um 50\u00a0Euro erh\u00f6hen w\u00fcrden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.840", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit w\u00fcrden Sie zeigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.240", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie in der Armutsdebatte wirklich etwas verstanden haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.880", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die FDP tr\u00e4gt nun hilfsweise vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.400", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Soliabschaffung sei wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit die Unternehmen die dringend n\u00f6tigen Investitionen in die Digitalisierung machen k\u00f6nnten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.720", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich appelliere an Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie als Partei weiterhin ernst genommen werden wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.360", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sollten Sie nicht jede Woche eine andere Steuersenkung mit der Digitalisierung begr\u00fcnden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.680", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Letztes Mal war von einer Sonder-AfA die Rede. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.880", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In dieser Woche ist es der Soli. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sollten sich entscheiden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.280", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im \u00dcbrigen braucht eine erfolgreiche Digitalisierungsstrategie mehr als ein F\u00fcllhorn von Steuersenkungen der FDP."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.400", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe mir die Zahlen genau angeschaut und will sie Ihnen nicht vorenthalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.160", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gewinne der Kapitalgesellschaften in Deutschland beliefen sich im vergangenen Jahr auf 550\u00a0Milliarden Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.840", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die ausgesch\u00fctteten Gewinne im letzten Jahr wurden auf 350\u00a0Milliarden Euro beziffert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.080", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der gezahlte Soli auf die zu entrichtende K\u00f6rperschaftsteuer belief sich auf ganze 2\u00a0Milliarden Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.200", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie der Wegfall dieser 2\u00a0Milliarden Euro den Investitionsschub bringen soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.760", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen selbst Sie angesichts der anderen Zahlen nicht begr\u00fcnden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.600", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ich habe die Zahlen zur K\u00f6rperschaftsteuer genannt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.960", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Richtig ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.480", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein vers\u00f6hnliches Ende\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die FDP und die CDU/CSU stehen bei der Bev\u00f6lkerung tats\u00e4chlich im Wort\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.560", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das hatten Sie angesprochen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.040", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie unter Helmut Kohl das Versprechen abgegeben hatten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.960", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es den Soli nur zeitlich befristet geben soll."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.080", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.960", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage des Kollegen Gottschalk?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.200", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich komme zum Schluss.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.960", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber genauso richtig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.920", 
   "id": "s000087", 
